params.description: A project ID or number. If specified, then export will attempt to write data to this project instead of the resource project. Otherwise, the resource project will be used.

params.name: data.dataset
params.description: Required. The name of the BigQuery dataset that the snapshot result should be exported to. If this dataset does not exist, the export call returns an INVALID_ARGUMENT error.
